import { useHistory } from 'react'
import Navibar from "./Navibar.css";
import { Navbar, Nav, Image} from "react-bootstrap";
import { PROFILE_ROUTE, ROOT_ROUTE } from '../utils/consts';
import { Link } from 'react-router-dom';


export default function NaviBar({name, img}) {
    const user = name ? true : false;
    return (
        <>
            <Navbar className="navbar navbar-dark bg--dark" bg="#000">
                <Navbar.Brand as={Link}>IT Cow</Navbar.Brand>
                <Navbar.Toggle aria-controls="navbar-collapse"/>
                <Navbar.Collapse>
                    <Nav className="mr-auto">
                        <Nav.Link onClick={() => history.push("/doctors")} >Выбрать врача</Nav.Link>
                        <Nav.Link>Выбрать симптомы</Nav.Link>
                        <Nav.Link>Бот консультант</Nav.Link>
                    </Nav>

                    <Nav>
                        { user ?
                            <Nav>
                                <Nav.Link exact to={PROFILE_ROUTE}>{name}</Nav.Link>
                                <Image src={img} roundedCircle/>
                            </Nav>
                            :
                            <Nav>
                                <Nav.Link>Регистрация</Nav.Link>
                                <Nav.Link>Войти</Nav.Link>
                            </Nav>
                        }  
                    </Nav>
                </Navbar.Collapse>
            </Navbar>
        </>
    )
}
